Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "department_id": 1,
  "ipcr_ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

### Get OPCR
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/pcr/opcr/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create IPCR
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/pcr/ipcr
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "main_task_ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

### Get IPCR
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/pcr/ipcr/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

